<P>
UNITED NATIONS, August 7 (Xinhua) -- A helicopter of the United
Nations Interim Force in Lebanon (UNIFIL) crashed on Wednesday
during a night training flight near a village of At Tiri in south
Lebanon, killing all five on broad, a statement by the UN
