freestyle. Men's 200 individual medley. Women's 200 individual
medley. Men's 50 freestyle. Women's 50 freestyle. Men's 200
breaststroke. Women's 200 breaststroke. Men's 1,500 freestyle.
Men's 4x100 medley relay. Women's 4x100 medley relay.
</P>
