<HEADLINE> Chinese Party Praises Indian Congress' Achievements </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CALCUTTA, August 8 (Xinhua) -- The Communist Party of China
(CPC) today praised the Indian Congress party, the second largest
party in India, for its achievements in various areas.
</P>
<P>
"For a long time, the Congress has made positive efforts and
gratifying achievements in maintaining national independence,
developing national economy and raising the living standards of
the Indian people," the CPC Central Committee said in a message to
