performances of its athletes can be matched by its ability to
stage the greatest sporting show on earth," he said.
</P>
<P>
South African National Olympic Committee Thursday admits the
country's bid logo -- the Olympic rings below the national flag.
</P>
<P>
The International Olympic Committee is due to announce the host
city for the 2004 Olympic game in Switzerland on September 5.
</P>
<P>
The other world cities bidding to host the game are Greek's
Athens, Argentina's Buenos Aires, Italy's Rome and Sweeden's
Stockholm. 
