<HEADLINE> Chinese Money Market Reports Thin Trading </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, August 8 (Xinhua/OANA) -- Turnover on the
Shanghai-based interbank money market plunged by more than 40
percent over the previous month to 5.831 billion yuan in July,
down 63.53 percent over the same period last year.
