<HEADLINE> Frequent Tourism Exchanges Between China, Australia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, August 8 (Xinhua) -- An increasing number of Chinese
are touring Australia, which has become a tourism magnet to
Chinese after Singapore, Malaysia and Thailand.
</P>
<P>
