<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Scenic Wuyi Mountain Well Protected </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, August 8 (Xinhua) -- As more and more tourists are
coming, the scenic Wuyi Mountain has become more conscious about
the protection of its natural environment.
</P>
<P>
As part of the protection effort, a new organization -- the
"Wuyi Mountain Scenic Area Protection Association" -- will
formally go into business on August 18.
</P>
<P>
In coastal Fujian province, Wuyi Mountain draws over one
million tourists every year by its natural beauty and numerous
sites of historical interest.
</P>
<P>
"While welcoming tourists to visit the mountain, we've always
attached great importance to the protection of the forests, the
soil, the water and the environment", an administrative official
told reporters.
</P>
<P>
Since the opening of the Wuyi Mountain Scenic Area in 1981,
efforts have been made to implement relevant State and local laws
governing the protection of the environment, the official said.
</P>
<P>
According to him, over 20 sets of local rules and regulations
have been promulgated so far for the protection of the mountain's
environment.
</P>
<P>
As a result, the mountain was sited by visiting officials of
the World Tourism Organization in 1990 as a "good example of
environmental protection of the world".
</P>
<P>
Officials believe that the inauguration of the new association
will be conducive to environmental protection. 
</P>
</TEXT>
