<HEADLINE> Beijing to Host International Autumn and Winter Clothing Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 8 (Xinhua) -- An international clothing and
accessories fair featuring autumn and winter collections is
scheduled for September 11-14 in Beijing, the country's first.
</P>
<P>
The event is sponsored by the China National Garment Research
and Design Center and China World Trade Center.
</P>
<P>
It will focus on autumn and winter collections and the latest
fashions to help promote the seasonal garment business and help
put China in contact with international ready-to-wear clothing
fairs.
</P>
